mlnorm
Copyright 2026 Jayashankar R

This product includes software for deterministic Malayalam Unicode normalization
(chillu atomization, ZWJ/ZWNJ handling, nta canonicalization, archaic/digit/
punctuation canonicalization, and conservative mojibake repair).

The normalization rules implemented here are restated facts about the Malayalam
script and the Unicode standard (see REFERENCES.md). No third-party text, tables,
code, or datasets are included or redistributed.

The only runtime dependency is `unicode-normalization` (MIT OR Apache-2.0).
